// src/pages/services/microwave-repair/not-heating.astro
// Wave 4b — failure-mode sub-service under residential microwave pillar.
// SEO: "microwave not heating", "microwave runs but doesn't heat",
// "magnetron failure", "microwave diode test".
// SAFETY: HV capacitor stores 4,000V even with unit unplugged for days.
// Customer DIY warning prominent.
// Roman tweak: Panasonic NN-SN/NN-SD inverter disambiguation — inverter board
