        <tr><td>HV capacitor</td><td>$260 to $440</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Door interlock switch (per switch)</td><td>$200 to $340</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Inverter board (Panasonic NN-SN/NN-SD, Samsung inverter)</td><td>$440 to $680</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Multi-component repair (year 9+)</td><td>$580 to $900</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty</td><td>90 days parts and labor</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="price-note">Residential $89 diagnostic, applied toward repair.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · Why us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Six reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>HV discharge protocol on every visit.</strong> Capacitor short through resistor before any high-voltage work. Industry-standard safety, not all shops follow it.</li>
      <li><strong>Component isolation testing.</strong> Magnetron, diode, capacitor, interlocks tested individually before any replacement. Prevents swap-and-pray.</li>
      <li><strong>Inverter architecture knowledge.</strong> Panasonic NN-SN/NN-SD and Samsung inverter models diagnosed correctly, not as traditional architecture.</li>
      <li><strong>Pro-style and drawer microwave expertise.</strong> Wolf MWD30, Sharp KB drawer, Miele M Touch built-in.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</strong> Verifiable.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> 24/7 phones, no emergency surcharge.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/services/microwave-repair/no-power/">no power</a>, <a href="/services/microwave-repair/plate-not-rotating/">plate not rotating</a>, <a href="/services/microwave-repair/sparking-arcing/">sparking / arcing (safety)</a>. Parent: <a href="/services/microwave-repair/">microwave repair</a>. Credentials: <a href="/credentials/licensed/">BHGS license</a>, <a href="/credentials/epa-certified/">EPA 608</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">09 · FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Microwave not heating, common questions.</h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
